{"data":[{"id":562129111,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"f9a23194de041b8f1f7346f0294f5819","url_token":"a-feng-34-23","name":"阿疯","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/f9a23194de041b8f1f7346f0294f5819","user_type":"people","headline":"工程师","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":3854,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562129111","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546055928,"updated_time":1546104126,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":5,"comment_count":0,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e我只是一个键盘数学家，不过我猜高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想不会被数学系录取。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e证明哥德巴赫猜想有多难我不知道，不过可以横向比较下。数学隐士格里戈里-佩雷尔曼证明证明庞加莱猜想。(因为格里戈里-佩雷尔曼真是隐居了，所以称为数学隐士。)\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e庞加莱猜想（Poincaré conjecture）是法国数学家庞加莱提出的一个猜想，是克雷数学研究所悬赏的七个千禧年大奖难题。其中三维的情形被俄罗斯数学家格里戈里·佩雷尔曼于\u003cb\u003e2003年左右证明\u003c/b\u003e。\u003cb\u003e2006年，数学界最终确认佩雷尔曼的证明解决了庞加莱猜想。\u003c/b\u003e庞加莱猜想是一个拓扑学中带有基本意义的命题，将有助于人类更好地研究三维空间，其带来的结果将会加深人们对流形性质的认识。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e格里戈里·佩雷尔曼在花了\u003cb\u003e8年时间研究这个足有一个世纪的数学难题\u003c/b\u003e后，在2002年11月和2003年7月之间，将3份关键论文的手稿粘贴到\u003ca href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//arXiv.org\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"invisible\"\u003ehttp://\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"visible\"\u003earXiv.org\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"invisible\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e这个专门刊登数学和物理预印本论文的网站上，并用电邮通知了几位数学家，声称自己证明了几何化猜想。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，大概是初中发论文，小学3年级你就开始研究这些高深谜题。小学3年级就开始研究这些高深的数学猜想，你大概率小学毕业就被中科大少年班挖走了，还上什么高什么中。你根本就没有机会上高中。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果你证明了任何数学猜想，直接发稿这个网站\u003ca href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//arxiv.org\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"invisible\"\u003ehttp://\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"visible\"\u003earxiv.org\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"invisible\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e免得被中科院的守门老大爷为难。\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"我只是一个键盘数学家，不过我猜高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想不会被数学系录取。证明哥德巴赫猜想有多难我不知道，不过可以横向比较下。数学隐士格里戈里-佩雷尔曼证明证明庞加莱猜想。(因为格里戈里-佩雷尔曼真是隐居了，所以称为数学隐士。)庞加莱猜想（Poin…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cba